		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You don't need discipline to finish things. You just need to pick projects that can be finished in days, rather than weeks. Or months. Or years.<br /><br />Anyone can remain focused for a few days. Figure out how long you can focus and then pick a project that takes half as long.

		

		</td>
